This apps is awesome. It is an overtraining but better over train then under train. Apply this with playing deviations and betting deviations you should be able to reduce the house edge down. With the right conditions you might even be able to walk home with some lunch money.

Great app!....the only thing that I would like to see is and ability to adjust a running count to a true count option and maybe an ace side count...

Great and easy app to use and learn the art of card counting. BUT, keep in mind it's only that, CARD COUNTING. It does not teach you how to play blackjack, use basic strategy, or use money management. It's main focus is just on card counting and if you practice and master the expert level it will truly sharpen your eyes and memory for counting cards.

Wow! This app is exactly as described! No, this is not a game. If you download this to play a card game, you will be quite confused and disappointed. This is an unmatchable knowledgeable experience, which allows you the challenge of applying your understanding, regarding how to keep a "True Count" of a 6-8 deck of cards. The implausible comments from our under-educated peers does not represent the experience of this simple app, which trains us easily, on how to keep a "Running Count"
Awesome

This app does a good job of overtraining a player to keep up with a fast count, which is good. You'll never encounter a game dealt this quickly at a casino (I never have), and if you drill with this app, you should have no problem keeping up at the tables. It would be nice if they implemented betting strategy.
